# Project Rules — My Personal Blog

## Project Info
- Owner: Do Duc Khanh Nguyen
- Type: Personal Blog & Portfolio
- Stack: Next.js 15, Tailwind CSS, JavaScript

## Code Rules
- Always use JavaScript, never TypeScript
- Always use Tailwind CSS, never write plain CSS
- Always use Next.js Image component for images, never <img> tag
- Always make UI responsive (mobile-first)
- Always add comments in English explaining each section

## Folder Structure
- Pages → app/
- Components → app/components/
- Images → public/images/
- API routes → app/api/

## Style Guide
- Color scheme: minimal, professional (vintage style)
- Font: clean, readable
- No unnecessary animations

## Important
- This is a portfolio site for a Transportation & Logistics Engineer    
- Keep code clean and well-structured
- Always explain what you built after each task